@iver56 
The cause is that the maximum width of `span` tag containing metric values is restricted to `120px`. So a metric value with many digits such as `1.11910480882216e-13` gets truncated and displayed incorrectly.

```javascript
const styles = {
  metricParamCellContent: {
    display: "inline-block",
    maxWidth: 120,
  },
};
```

https://github.com/mlflow/mlflow/blob/master/mlflow/server/js/src/components/BaggedCell.js#L7-L12


```javascript
            ...
            <span
              className="metric-param-value run-table-container"
              style={styles.metricParamCellContent}
            >
              {value}
            </span>
            ...
```

https://github.com/mlflow/mlflow/blob/master/mlflow/server/js/src/components/BaggedCell.js#L76--L81
